{"tid":333324,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個同屋企人去旅行嘅崩潰經歷","createTime":"2017-07-23T16:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T14:20:00.000Z","uid":36025,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d12d6d30842c92d9f0f6904307350fe5f918b340","tid":333324,"uid":36025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T16:52:07.000Z","msg":"自由行，家人行得勁快成日差d走失，雖然唔係年紀好大但係係言語不通嘅國家令我十分擔心又狂追狂叫停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每20-30分鐘要去一次廁所，但又係突然勁快咁行消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後尾諗番起可能係身體開始差，所以話比自己知要多d留意家人"},{"pid":"5998873288119fdea4aeec4684f174014cdab80c","tid":333324,"uid":45431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T16:54:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自由行，家人行得勁快成日差d走失，雖然唔係年紀好大但係係言語不通嘅國家令我十分擔心又狂追狂叫停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每20-30分鐘要去一次廁所，但又係突然勁快咁行消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後尾諗番起可能係身體開始差，所以話比自己知要多d留意家人</blockquote><br />\n所以同老人家去旅行就join團啦，自由行真係搵黎搞"},{"pid":"b7b105b1f4edf7b836865e73227d607a1f3fc3aa","tid":333324,"uid":36025,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T16:57:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自由行，家人行得勁快成日差d走失，雖然唔係年紀好大但係係言語不通嘅國家令我十分擔心又狂追狂叫停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每20-30分鐘要去一次廁所，但又係突然勁快咁行消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後尾諗番起可能係身體開始差，所以話比自己知要多d留意家人</blockquote><br />\n所以同老人家去旅行就join團啦，自由行真係搵黎搞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n家人唔老先4x-5x左右，又唔想跟團想自己有得簡行程，唯有做下孝子帶佢自由行，雖然好崩潰，但係佢講番起有去過咩地方時個樣好開心，再黎一次都會自由行嘅"},{"pid":"c3cea4dbcd5ce64f9ef90cb6e51d0c44c4c7b84b","tid":333324,"uid":96146,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:06:39.000Z","msg":"同老母去台灣自由行<br />\n去之前乜都話好 冇所謂 <br />\n去到又嫌貴 又嫌悶<br />\n想買件褸都話點解唔返香港買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後來陪佢跟團去北京 <br />\n成團都係師奶阿叔 又要去埋個d購物點<br />\n買左一堆茶葉 中成藥 浸腳藥粉 洗左我萬幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5日4夜內 我唯一睇中既街邊小飾物$30 佢又嫌貴 唔比我買 <span style=\"font-size: small;\">雖然佢後尾偷偷買左比我</span><br />\n<br />\n從此之後 我都盡量避免同佢去旅行 寧願比錢佢同班師奶出去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">但出年我又要帶佢去歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"249157ecbc07e93c089e74d8281a5c248e8a9ec9","tid":333324,"uid":36025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:14:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同老母去台灣自由行<br />\n去之前乜都話好 冇所謂 <br />\n去到又嫌貴 又嫌悶<br />\n想買件褸都話點解唔返香港買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後來陪佢跟團去北京 <br />\n成團都係師奶阿叔 又要去埋個d購物點<br />\n買左一堆茶葉 中成藥 浸腳藥粉 洗左我萬幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5日4夜內 我唯一睇中既街邊小飾物$30 佢又嫌貴 唔比我買 <span style=\"font-size: small;\">雖然佢後尾偷偷買左比我</span><br />\n<br />\n從此之後 我都盡量避免同佢去旅行 寧願比錢佢同班師奶出去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">但出年我又要帶佢去歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 台灣個part我都有經歷過<br />\n聽親跟團去北京都係買補品<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過都偷偷地買左小飾物比你都幾窩心呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你仲有半年至一年時間心理準備，影多d相之後睇番，可能會有唔同感覺"},{"pid":"7bccaa101ecefb58ea2f0ac21f679003b7563890","tid":333324,"uid":56505,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:15:13.000Z","msg":"同老母家姐去<br />\n2 個嘈架  我夾係中間on99<br />\n唔會有第2 次"},{"pid":"98a952cfd02b71f95684c6c56846af6264797adc","tid":333324,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:18:08.000Z","msg":"老母同啊哥係英國鬧交到依家返左黎兩個月冇講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93caef98ae18782fabdd5eaa9ac17132d6126cc0","tid":333324,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:25:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同老母去台灣自由行<br />\n去之前乜都話好 冇所謂 <br />\n去到又嫌貴 又嫌悶<br />\n想買件褸都話點解唔返香港買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後來陪佢跟團去北京 <br />\n成團都係師奶阿叔 又要去埋個d購物點<br />\n買左一堆茶葉 中成藥 浸腳藥粉 洗左我萬幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5日4夜內 我唯一睇中既街邊小飾物$30 佢又嫌貴 唔比我買 <span style=\"font-size: small;\">雖然佢後尾偷偷買左比我</span><br />\n<br />\n從此之後 我都盡量避免同佢去旅行 寧願比錢佢同班師奶出去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">但出年我又要帶佢去歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 台灣個part我都有經歷過<br />\n聽親跟團去北京都係買補品<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過都偷偷地買左小飾物比你都幾窩心呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你仲有半年至一年時間心理準備，影多d相之後睇番，可能會有唔同感覺</blockquote><br />\n冇計 歐洲跟團又on99 佢又唔識英文 <br />\n就算佢識英文都唔敢比佢跟埋班師奶去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有我帶佢去 依家努力灌輸佢歐洲旅行知識 希望到時唔會咁多伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb1b6043052d10221626e3f2c1e770ee31aa59a","tid":333324,"uid":64469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:30:45.000Z","msg":"同老豆搭凌晨機，好多人都訓晒，我地未訓佢就係咁同我講野，佢又唔係真係好大聲但全機都好靜既時候佢一講野就感覺佢把聲好突出，個下真係好驚佢嘈到其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16341195fcc891a4e6c66e6fde9512433c5d8c93","tid":333324,"uid":92468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:30:54.000Z","msg":"以後想要呢啲機會都冇得要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d722808da91214d60d1b6d899ead9765ef769267","tid":333324,"uid":36025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:54:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老母同啊哥係英國鬧交到依家返左黎兩個月冇講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩事搞到咁呀"},{"pid":"b29ef02fb7dd3d5e4d1a71aca8aaf70e898dc079","tid":333324,"uid":36025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:57:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同老母去台灣自由行<br />\n去之前乜都話好 冇所謂 <br />\n去到又嫌貴 又嫌悶<br />\n想買件褸都話點解唔返香港買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後來陪佢跟團去北京 <br />\n成團都係師奶阿叔 又要去埋個d購物點<br />\n買左一堆茶葉 中成藥 浸腳藥粉 洗左我萬幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5日4夜內 我唯一睇中既街邊小飾物$30 佢又嫌貴 唔比我買 <span style=\"font-size: small;\">雖然佢後尾偷偷買左比我</span><br />\n<br />\n從此之後 我都盡量避免同佢去旅行 寧願比錢佢同班師奶出去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">但出年我又要帶佢去歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 台灣個part我都有經歷過<br />\n聽親跟團去北京都係買補品<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過都偷偷地買左小飾物比你都幾窩心呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你仲有半年至一年時間心理準備，影多d相之後睇番，可能會有唔同感覺</blockquote><br />\n冇計 歐洲跟團又on99 佢又唔識英文 <br />\n就算佢識英文都唔敢比佢跟埋班師奶去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有我帶佢去 依家努力灌輸佢歐洲旅行知識 希望到時唔會咁多伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 孝子系列！我都未去過歐遊，如果我去完都會想帶家人去下，開下眼界"},{"pid":"6e93556a89023c2eb7325abd5174fccdd6eabeb4","tid":333324,"uid":36025,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同老豆搭凌晨機，好多人都訓晒，我地未訓佢就係咁同我講野，佢又唔係真係好大聲但全機都好靜既時候佢一講野就感覺佢把聲好突出，個下真係好驚佢嘈到其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次你都訓埋，呢啲情況尷尬d"},{"pid":"18427d4c7016aeb393d47376354433bd7bb54716","tid":333324,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:00:25.000Z","msg":"細個去台灣跟團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05503682a6ac5abd335f22eedc4f6bd9925122f","tid":333324,"uid":51981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:01:04.000Z","msg":"親戚成日去日本 婆婆就係咁講要跟埋去<br />\n終於有次同埋佢去 聽講佢由第一日就一路嘈<br />\n返到黎係咁同人講其實佢唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似迫佢去咁<br />\n <br />\n佢勁怕曬 但親戚去越南玩佢又要跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講明越南曬到仆街都要去 返到黎嘈足一個月話自己曬傷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有跟團會去購物點 佢去親去要買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c513c2e6b8ff4b6d6df5eb552d9074c40ccb271","tid":333324,"uid":36025,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:02:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以後想要呢啲機會都冇得要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就係好怕面對死亡，所以經常比定心理準備自己，就算覺得會崩潰都要帶兩老旅行，好多回憶係一世嘅擺係心度"},{"pid":"c4bc5f8960c37155d5a0c9582bd55494cde8f3c6","tid":333324,"uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:03:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個去台灣跟團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都試過 成班人年紀最細果個都讀緊小學高年級<br />\n跟團要去個on9 lego land 入面得幼稚園學生先岩玩既野<br />\n結果成班人on99咁坐係Starbucks 等上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7a6f3fc40e0c07014e8c49ded6c5044ca7da61","tid":333324,"uid":36025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>親戚成日去日本 婆婆就係咁講要跟埋去<br />\n終於有次同埋佢去 聽講佢由第一日就一路嘈<br />\n返到黎係咁同人講其實佢唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似迫佢去咁<br />\n <br />\n佢勁怕曬 但親戚去越南玩佢又要跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講明越南曬到仆街都要去 返到黎嘈足一個月話自己曬傷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有跟團會去購物點 佢去親去要買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 婆婆邊到鄉下？不如香港同鄉下來回算"},{"pid":"a3117e4767772dffbf6e603b74df9dc1cc12cbde","tid":333324,"uid":29523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:08:39.000Z","msg":"去到老母失控亂發脾氣，平日忍耐力好高既老豆都爆seed鬧交，返到香港幾乎變單親家庭，夠爆未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a782c812df5f21def67f38588460a64e8133833","tid":333324,"uid":51981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:09:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>親戚成日去日本 婆婆就係咁講要跟埋去<br />\n終於有次同埋佢去 聽講佢由第一日就一路嘈<br />\n返到黎係咁同人講其實佢唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似迫佢去咁<br />\n <br />\n佢勁怕曬 但親戚去越南玩佢又要跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講明越南曬到仆街都要去 返到黎嘈足一個月話自己曬傷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有跟團會去購物點 佢去親去要買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 婆婆邊到鄉下？不如香港同鄉下來回算</blockquote><br />\n天津人 佢返天津會嫌悶同夏天太熱冬天太凍<br />\n公公成日都忍唔住屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c84c08760d973b000de95b461d5e4afd9395c0","tid":333324,"uid":36025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:11:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去到老母失控亂發脾氣，平日忍耐力好高既老豆都爆seed鬧交，返到香港幾乎變單親家庭，夠爆未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因咩事會亂發脾氣呀？"},{"pid":"d6417d1cf40a1e49826bc7d11065f109db8f1396","tid":333324,"uid":28814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:17:42.000Z","msg":"同親老母旅行佢都會叫曬佢啲朋友去<br />\n佢朋友又帶埋啲十一二歲嘅仔女去<br />\n嘈撚到仆街<br />\n三個人去旅行變十鳩幾個人<br />\n成日係唔知邊到聽人地話靚就想去<br />\n試過係台北坐幾個鐘車去台中睇日月潭<br />\n嚟緊去韓國都唔知點編行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c973a5099bc8b1c55d240457fde971452327d0a","tid":333324,"uid":77661,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:28:19.000Z","msg":"一家人去台灣五日 比老母屌足五日<br />\n已經全程的士代步咁濟<br />\n有陣時企係十字路口到搵路企左十秒都冇已經比佢屌到上天<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要搭的士果陣死要面 同司機吹水講起兩地既屋既面積 佢就係到吹水話香港既屋好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a152425fffc3b3027818f2b43fc77608a2ea870b","tid":333324,"uid":36025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T00:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同親老母旅行佢都會叫曬佢啲朋友去<br />\n佢朋友又帶埋啲十一二歲嘅仔女去<br />\n嘈撚到仆街<br />\n三個人去旅行變十鳩幾個人<br />\n成日係唔知邊到聽人地話靚就想去<br />\n試過係台北坐幾個鐘車去台中睇日月潭<br />\n嚟緊去韓國都唔知點編行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個又係經典，我都聽唔少一大班人會一齊去，成個感覺都崩潰<br />\n<br />\n編行程同帶團真係做免費導遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce86b1f0668b8a06044522ec0f1b99b43c9c7ca","tid":333324,"uid":1495,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T00:07:35.000Z","msg":"去日本旅行食魚生飯做早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經講咗我胃唔好，都幫我嗌個鐵火丼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都係好想同佢哋去多啲地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3746e82bfd506c27ae1143154a6dbdf715e3b3","tid":333324,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T00:13:39.000Z","msg":"同老母去過幾次旅行 幾次都病<br />\n有一次佢自己話要去泡菜國 然後自己頂唔順嗰邊啲乾燥 搞到流左少少鼻血 之後狂鬧話早知唔黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3261358747e8e249ee940a9d4c4485d711832c3","tid":333324,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T00:13:55.000Z","msg":"一係租車，一係跟團。<br />\n<br />\n有咩事都可以叫老人家係車休息下"},{"pid":"0588c7216ebbe8e227f707df9c23679afb86524a","tid":333324,"uid":22844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T00:18:18.000Z","msg":"發咗老豆老母同幾個親戚去咗幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢哋五條友都唔識英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾次都去到崩潰邊緣 覺得自己eq去到